    <h1>Star Rating</h1>
    <p class="description">A 1-to-5 scale review score displayed in Google search results, Maps, and the Local Pack. Star ratings displayed as <strong>rich snippets boost CTR by 15-30%</strong> and are a confirmed ranking factor in Google Business Profile rankings.</p>
